00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,720
 you need to find a partner,

298
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:52,400
 and you need to make sure to look for marriage,

299
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:54,960
 to have a fulfilling and complete human experience,

300
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:58,920
 you, if you have Jesus, can say, no, I'm good.

301
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:01,980
 I've got everything I need.

302
00:12:01,980 --> 00:12:04,780
 I'm not one who is needy like the rest of the world

303
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:06,300
 that subscribes to your advice

304
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:08,340
 because I have all that I need in him.

