00:12:08,340 --> 00:12:11,220
 I have one who stabilizes me.

306
00:12:11,220 --> 00:12:13,220
 I have one who leads me forward.

307
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:14,640
 I have one who works all things,

308
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:17,820
 even the bad of my life into good purpose.

