00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,440
 And the reason why all this is true

345
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,840
 is because dating is anxiety-inducing.

346
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:49,520
 Like it leaves people so pent up and worried.

