00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:50,440
 because 63%, not seven out of 10, but six out of 10 men

368
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:52,240
 are just opting to stay single

369
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:55,760
 given the difficulties they find in the dating world.

