00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:10,760
 Seeking out love, searching for the one,

376
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:13,720
 sharing your feelings, risking rejection,

377
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:16,280
 and processing the possibility of forever

378
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:19,840
 with someone leaves people feeling anxious.

379
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:23,560
 And yet here's the thing for the believer,

380
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:28,400
 as we set sail and we voyage into the sea

381
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:30,960
 of swirling emotion and capsizing doubt

