00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:37,440
 we have a steady anchor.

384
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:40,320
 We have one who holds us fast

385
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:44,000
 because we don't depend upon our strength in the storm.

386
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,800
 We depend on his.

387
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:49,560
 We know one who calms the winds and the waves,

388
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:52,640
 even whenever the hurricane of romance blows through.

