00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:01,960
 He says in Philippians 4, six through seven, famous verse,

393
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:05,640
 "Do not be anxious about anything,

394
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:07,680
 "but in everything by prayer and supplication

395
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:11,280
 "with thanksgiving," those are deeds of dependence.

396
00:16:11,280 --> 00:16:13,120
 "Let your requests be made known to God

397
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:15,300
 "and the peace of God, which surpasses all understanding,

