00:16:20,880 --> 00:16:24,120
 you move from an obsession to that which isn't.

401
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,440
 I don't have a boyfriend, I don't have a girlfriend,

402
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,280
 I'm gonna be alone forever.

403
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:27,800
 All I'm gonna have around my house are cats.

404
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:30,680
 You move from an obsession with what isn't

