00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:33,040
 to a gratitude for what is,

406
00:16:33,040 --> 00:16:36,740
 that I may not have a significant other,

407
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:41,880
 but I do have the significant one.

408
00:16:41,880 --> 00:16:45,500
 I have God, and he is all I need.

409
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:48,160
 I need nothing else, for in him,

410
00:16:48,160 --> 00:16:52,040
 I find all that I want and require.

